column5: Looking for accomadations on the lake in Northern Ontario. Anyone have any suggestions? Would be great to sleep 6 and have its own dock. Not interested in fishing lodges (to costly), but would like to fish.
Take a look at the various resorts on the west end of Lac Seul.
Hi Sydney<I don't know how far north you are looking butI have a cabin on Rainy Lake for rent by the week [email protected]
go to "noto.com" for the nothern ontario tourist outfitter listings or call 1800-ontario for the booklet.
